OL,6,FI cannot help but wonder if the
OL,7,Fregional opts during ITV Breakfast are
OL,8,Fon borrowed time though. This change
OL,9,Fmight be right for Good Morning
OL,10,FBritain as a whole and its audience `
OL,11,Fyou hardly notice that the 8.10am
OL,12,Fbulletin has gone ` but it also risks
OL,13,Fmarginalising the bulletins.
OL,15,FFor the first 10 years of breakfast
OL,16,FTV, the franchise was held by TV-am
OL,17,Fwhich did not include regional news
OL,18,Fbulletins. The regional opts were an
OL,19,Fimportant part of the BBC's breakfast
OL,20,Foffering from day one.
