OL,6,FOn ITV, the regional bulletins arrived
OL,7,Fin 1993 with GMTV. The company's
OL,8,Fbackers saw this as a positive
OL,9,Fimprovement ` evidence they might
OL,10,Fprovide a better service than TV-am.
OL,12,FWhile generally the 1991 franchise
OL,13,Fround did viewers and those who
OL,14,Fbelieve in public service broadcasting
OL,15,Fno favours, there's no doubt the
OL,16,Fintroduction of regional news to ITV's
OL,17,Fbreakfast hours was a good move.
OL,19,FBut the service was in addition to the
OL,20,Flegal commitments to local news
OL,21,Fcarried by the regional Channel 3
OL,22,Fcompanies.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G4/8
