OL,6,FThere were contracts to provide the
OL,7,Flocal service ` usually given to the
OL,8,Fregional C3 companies but for many
OL,9,Fyears UTV did not provide the early
OL,10,Fmorning bulletins in Northern Ireland
OL,11,Fand STV lost the Scottish contract for
OL,12,Fa period.
OL,14,FThe changes to the format last week
OL,15,Fundoubtedly reduce the potential reach
OL,16,Ffor the bulletins ` anyone who
OL,17,Fswitches on after 7.15am will miss
OL,18,Fthem.
OL,20,FThere is no evidence so far of an
OL,21,Fadverse audience reaction.
