OL,6,FWho's to say whether, in the medium to
OL,7,Flong term, ITV may look at whether the
OL,8,Fremaining opts are necessary and an
OL,9,Fappropriate use of resources, then
OL,10,Fdiscuss the matter with Ofcom.
OL,12,FWould the remaining bulletins be
OL,13,Fmissed? Could the resources be moved
OL,14,Fto the main regional bulletins on ITV
OL,15,F1 later in the day or spent on the
OL,16,Fcompany's news website and app?
OL,18,FBut does the change to Good Morning
OL,19,FBritain provide the BBC with an
OL,20,Fopportunity?
