OL,3,CGood Morning Britain drops regional
OL,4,Cnews bulletin
OL,6,FThere is no doubt that regional
OL,7,Fbulletins are an important part of BBC
OL,8,FBreakfast and valued by its audience.
OL,10,FThe bulletins were missed when they
OL,11,Fdisappeared during the pandemic.
OL,13,FPolitically, the BBC needs to provide
OL,14,Fearly morning news in the nations.
OL,15,FPractically, they are valued by
OL,16,Fviewers across the UK.
OL,18,FThe 7.55am opt was reinstated by
OL,19,Fpublic demand and the last bulletin of
OL,20,Fthe morning at around 9.15am was
OL,21,Flengthened when the programme was
OL,22,Fextended earlier this year.
